   - If token entry required: enters token on the page and clicks Verify
5) Step 3: User enters new password and confirms
6) Strength meter gives live feedback; upon valid submission, password is set
7) User is logged in or prompted to log in; confirmation screen shows success and actions
8) All steps produce audit logs for compliance and can be reversed if required

